Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.70,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3600)\bord2.25\3c&H1F1F1F&\be6\c&HFFFFFC&}so ra no wo to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:13.52,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:22.91,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:28.12,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.34,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:46.28,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, the happiness they sang about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:55.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:01:00.62,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:06.08,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:15.55,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:27.51,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this gentle light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:01.95,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}First Battle - About a Chair
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:46.42,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:49.21,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.56,0:23:07.69,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:13.66,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:22.50,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:26.63,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:28.32,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:32.61,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:33.93,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:39.94,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.97,0:23:39.94,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:45.77,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:45.77,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:52.15,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.15,0:23:57.90,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:02.54,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:42.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be practicing with only the mouthpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.49,0:01:47.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:55.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I would love to play tunes like you, Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:57.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My way is Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:02:00.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:02.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the mess hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:05.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:15.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Craggy, and rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:22.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:38.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:16.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we prepared all this for your arrival last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A sort of welcome meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:22.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:25.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring in the fish I was drying upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:27.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:33.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At least eat breakfast before you sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:43.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:44.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Rio's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The food's going to get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:10.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me reintroduce you to the members of Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First, our commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:19.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Filicia Heidemann, tank commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun while you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël Kannagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Corporal Kannagi. Pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:50.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's our mechanic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:03.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Kureha Suminoya. Gunner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:12.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be younger than you, but I have seniority. You'd better listen to everyt-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran out of gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up the good work, Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, how about breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:30.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:38.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:48.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I made the bacon myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:49.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat as much as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:50.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:53.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Both soldiers and buglers are all about body strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:55.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up and build it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:16.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When breakfast is over, show her around the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:27.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:34.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I had work to do, but this was an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:37.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm showing you around, under orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:40.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Insubordination, Private Sorami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:44.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:45.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Suminoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:52.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First: attention to the national and platoon flags!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:57.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:02.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tank Platoon 1121
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:06.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,currently consists of five members, by rank: one lieutenant,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,one sergeant, one corporal,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,two privates. Total: five.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:15.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Private Suminoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:19.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be the minimum number for a platoon, but it does mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the few and the proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:25.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:30.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our platoon has been equipped with the following armaments:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:31.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One tank,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,one heavy machine gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,two light machine guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,four rifles,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and five handguns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:46.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our assignment is to defend the national borders of Seize, Trois, with these arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:53.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Suminoya! I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Permission to speak granted, Private Sorami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:05.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If my memory serves me, then next to Seize is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:10.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, beyond the mountains is Nomansland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:15.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the borders of Helvetia only extend to this region, so this is the national border!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The front lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:19.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A strategic position!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not allow a pre-emptive strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We trade off watch duty through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:25.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping is strictly forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:31.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the only hotline connecting to the capital in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:37.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If it rings, something big is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If it does, everyone is to be woken up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and immediately placed on full alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:43.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:46.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Private Suminoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:06.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,On the second floor are the Commander's quarters and the operations room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:08.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Entrance is strictly-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But make sure you knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the latrines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:19.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Readying the bath and cleaning are done in turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The bathing order is by rank, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:30.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's more fun if everyone bathes together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:37.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But today is Noël's turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But she looks tired today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:48.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, if you're like that, the recruit will never learn discipline!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:53.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it later, so be commander-like and stay firm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:16.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, take a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:21.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the tank deployed for Platoon 1121's use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:24.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Zero Series Autonomous Walker Tank, the Takemicaduchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so much bigger than the ones at training!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:33.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of those zero-generation tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:37.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are less than ten still in operation in the country. A treasure from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:40.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're supposed to be really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But its legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:48.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's undergoing repairs, but we don't have enough parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:56.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And we don't have the servicing manual and we can't find any parts for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:11:00.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but Noël is doing something about it, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:03.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just decoration!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:06.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:10.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This tank... I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:15.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're lax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:21.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, our unit is completely lax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:25.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They even call us Seize's extra baggage or a decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:29.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got pink epaulettes and we don't even have an operational tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:30.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:32.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:34.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for the tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:40.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're already getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:42.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:45.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like us when we had just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:47.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:51.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:55.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After you sent Kanata to sleep last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:59.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, why did we get communications personnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:03.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You said the new recruit would be a loader or a pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:08.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters sent her to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:11.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't always get what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:11.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there now. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio will take care of you the way she always has.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like she always has.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's young, but she has good intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:31.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She might already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:33.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:36.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:42.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What appeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:53.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3\pos(1840,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:58.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1\pos(80,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:00.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:12.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You were seeing things half asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:13.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:15.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, you thought so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the ghost, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in the barracks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going along with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's normal for ghosts to be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:31.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you stop playing along with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:33.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And Noël, I'm disappointed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:37.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an engineer! You're supposed to \N investigate this scientifically before reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:38.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:45.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no such things as ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:46.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No such things, no such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No possible way there are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:58.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with you completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. There are no such things as ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:03.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance of a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:05.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:10.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspect the area thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:13.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In the event you encounter the enemy, blow your bugle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:15.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll send you reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:22.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:25.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kana- Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:26.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:37.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The thunder is like a marching beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:39.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:41.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Kana-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:43.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Sorami! You take the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:45.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:46.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:05.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This part was left the way it was before it was turned into a fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:12.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I would know? Just hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:40.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideographs...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:45.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't read it, there's no point staring at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:48.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be wonderful if I could read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:51.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just nonsense from a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:52.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:01.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How can't you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:08.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But ghosts are things that protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:15.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In the village I was born, we had a festival every year to thank the ghosts that protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:17.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of village would do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:26.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. Ghosts possess people, drink blood, move corpses, and are just pure evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:45.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes rats can carry diseases-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Well, aren't you sca-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:11.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:22.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this was a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:29.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There probably isn't a school this big, even in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:33.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But there used to be a lot more people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:39.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm sure that this building was filled with kids about our age,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and they would study together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:45.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have taught music here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:49.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't read the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:06.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,D-sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:32.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you just smiling like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:36.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wonderful, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:37.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What part?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:38.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:45.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The town of Seize, this fortress, \N everyone in our platoon. All of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:54.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just a tiny little unit in the middle of nowhere that doesn't even matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our tank is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:01.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And they forget to send us supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:05.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just soldiers in name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're completely lax.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:09.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:17.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:18.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:31.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:46.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:52.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the wonderful, ever so wonderful, Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm the gunner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:03.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is our ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the "ghost" part?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:11.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:14.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You look just like that thief from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You...You're dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:21.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't frighten her when she's hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:28.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably just doesn't have a place to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And what was our unit's symbol?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Making roasted owl is like roasting ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it, Shuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She gave it a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:44.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:48.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know you nearly died yesterday because of this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:52.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I got to have an amazing adventure because of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:54.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:21:00.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the furthest thing from an adventure there could be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:04.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. Maybe we should be democratic about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:06.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:11.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But if she steals food again, then she'll be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:13.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:21:59.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you played this morning, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:02.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The townspeople would complain if we let Kanata play it every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:04.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:12.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:19.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:24.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to find another one of these chairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.31,0:22:26.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it for you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:28.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:33.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:34.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:37.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.66,0:22:39.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:14.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(960,404)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: A Day in the Life - Rio Runs
